{
  "script_id": "reuleaux",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "要让形状滚动时高度不变，你大概只会想到圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "可是除了圆，还有一大类曲线也能做到处处等宽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "其中最著名的，是一个鼓起肚子的三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "construct-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/construct-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "取一个正三角形，以每个顶点为圆心，边长为半径画弧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "construct-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/construct-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "三段圆弧首尾相接，就围成了鼓起的勒洛三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "construct-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/construct-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "同样的办法用在正五边形、正七边形上，也能得到等宽曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "width",
      "line_id": "wid-1",
      "filename": "width-wid-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/width-wid-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "用两条平行线把它夹住，一条切着弧，一条正好压着对面的顶点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "width",
      "line_id": "wid-2",
      "filename": "width-wid-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/width-wid-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "这个距离刚好等于半径，无论你从哪个方向去夹，都一模一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "width",
      "line_id": "wid-3",
      "filename": "width-wid-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/width-wid-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "巴比尔定理还告诉我们，它的周长恒等于圆周率乘以宽度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "roll",
      "line_id": "roll-1",
      "filename": "roll-roll-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/roll-roll-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "让它在两条平行线间滚动，顶部始终贴着上线，高度纹丝不动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "roll",
      "line_id": "roll-2",
      "filename": "roll-roll-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/roll-roll-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "可它的形心却在上下颠簸，所以做车轮会让人晃得难受。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "roll",
      "line_id": "roll-3",
      "filename": "roll-roll-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/roll-roll-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "但反过来，这份等宽让钻头能钻出近似方形的孔，硬币也能等宽异形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "切换三、五、七条边，看不同的勒洛多边形如何都保持等宽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "点开滚动动画，盯住顶端和中心，感受高度不变而形心起伏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "等宽曲线在任何方向上被夹住的宽度都相同，圆只是其中一员。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "勒洛三角形由三段圆弧拼成，周长恒为圆周率乘宽度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "reuleaux",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/reuleaux/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "简单的圆弧，藏着钻方孔的巧思，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.11000000000001,
  "total_size": 577728
}